    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">How does RFID attendance tracking work?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">RFID attendance tracking uses radio frequency identification technology. Each user has an RFID card or tag with a unique identifier. When this tag comes in proximity to an RFID reader, it registers attendance automatically in the system.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Can I integrate this system with my existing software?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, our RFID attendance system offers robust API integration capabilities that allow you to connect it with your existing HR systems, student management software, and other enterprise applications.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">How secure is the RFID technology?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Our RFID system employs advanced encryption and security protocols to protect data. The cards themselves use encrypted communication, and the system includes anti-cloning features to prevent unauthorized duplication.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">What happens if someone forgets their RFID card?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">The system includes manual override options for administrators to record attendance for users who forget their cards. We also offer temporary card solutions and mobile app alternatives.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="#" class="text-green-500 font-medium hover:underline">View All FAQs →</a>
    </div>
</section>

